forward to Purgatory and Paradise (e.g., }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Inf}{\plain \fs24 \f1 . I.118-129; }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Inf}{\plain \fs24 \f1 . II.71-74), while }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Purgatorio}{\plain \fs24 \f1  I \softline
