commentators would seem to believe that Dante is here alluding only to Paul's heavenly journey, \softline
not to his aprocryphal descent.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab For }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Vas d'elez{\f3 \'56}one}{\plain \fs24 \f1  (Chosen Vessel) see Acts 9:15.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \par
