}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b\f1 48.}{\plain \fs24 \f1   For a possible source for this verse, not hitherto cited, see }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Aeneid}{\plain \fs24 \f1  X.592-593, where \softline
