}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f1 \ul0 \tab 52.}{\plain \fs24 \f1   The verbal adjective }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 sospesi}{\plain \fs24 \f1  (suspended), that is, in a position between the presence \softline
of God and actual punishment, is a technical term for those who dwell in Limbo.  See Mazzoni's \softline
