}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b\f1 53-54.}{\plain \fs24 \f1   Beatrice's anonymous first appearance and Virgil's instinctive obeisance might \softline
easily lead a reader to assume an 'allegorical' valence for this lady.  For a recent study of the roots \softline
