[1958]),  pp. 65-66; and to Giuseppe Mazzota, }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Dante, Poet of the Desert}{\plain \fs24 \f1  (Princeton: Princeton \softline
University Press, 1979), pp. 157-58).\par
